            <p class="post-sub-text">G'day. I'm a digital experience consultant who focuses on the intersection of business, technology, and customer. I come from a background in software development - having a greater context of how digital solutions work allows me to work closely with both business and IT stakeholders.
</br></br>I am a problem solver, an adaptable and reliable team member who is unafraid to take initiative to understand and identify opportunities for improvement. I understand the value of empathy, listening, communication, trust - especially in team settings and in stakeholder management.
</p> 
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sphhuynh/" class="link text-button" rel="bookmark">CONNECT WITH ME ON LINKEDIN {% include "icons/arrow.svg" %}</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="special-page bottom">
        {{ content | safe }}
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
{% endblock %}

